title: Static Analysis

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

android.permission.GET_TASKS.description: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS.info: use the authentication credentials of an account
android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS.description: Allows an application to request authentication tokens.

android.permission.REORDER_TASKS.description: Allows an application to move tasks to the foreground and background. Malicious applications can force themselves to the front without your control.

android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD.description: Allows an application to disable the key lock and any associated password security. A legitimate example of this is the phone disabling the key lock when receiving an incoming phone call, then re-enabling the key lock when the call is finished.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS.description: Allows application to modify global audio settings, such as volume and routing.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.description: Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

android.permission.CHANGE_CONFIGURATION.description: Allows an application to change the current configuration, such as the locale or overall font size.

android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to access the list of accounts known by the phone.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

free.music.tube.player.permission.C2D_ME.description: Allows the application to receive push notifications.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

"faq_activity_content1" : "1) Please check whether your Internet connection is still working
2) If your Internet connection is normal, please try to force quitting & reload the app."

"faq_activity_content10" : "1) Tap the playlist you want to edit
2) Tap "Edit" next to the playlist title
3) Tap "Delete Playlist" and then "OK" to delete the playlist"

"faq_activity_content11" : "1) Tap the playlist you want to edit
2) Tap "Edit" next to the playlist title
3) Drag the ≡ icons to rearrange song order, then tap "Done" to save."

"faq_activity_content12" : "If you're using cellular networks, please switch to WIFI or move to a location with better cellular networks connection and see if it improves. If you turn off "HD Video and Audio" in More tab, it will also help!"
"faq_activity_content13" : "You can use the volume toggle of your device to adjust the volume."

"faq_activity_content14" : "Free Music will not post your activity to Facebook unless you authorize it. If you login with your Facebook account and would like to automatically share your activities on Facebook, you can turn on "Post activities to Facebook" in the More tab. You can also hide your activities by turning off "Post activities to Facebook"."

"faq_activity_content15" : "If you have further questions or suggestions, please leave a message at Free Music Fan Page:https://www.facebook.com/topfreemusic or send an email to <topfreemusicteam@gmail.com>. Please also mention your device information. We will give a feedback to you as soon as possible!"

"faq_activity_content2" : "The YouTube video uploader may restrict the video by channel and by region. For example, certain videos are restricted to YouTube only or to specific regions. When this happens, you may encounter some playback issues. In that case, please try to search for other video sources."
"faq_activity_content3" : "Due to the abnormality of Facebook login system recently, the authorization page may go blank. If this happens, please restart Free Music and login again."

"faq_activity_content4" : "According to YouTube's guideline, videos must be streamed directly from YouTube, so Internet connection is required to play videos.Therefore, Free Music does NOT support downloading YouTube content for offline listening."

"faq_activity_content5" : "Please search for "keywords", then select "show all song results". You should be able to find the song you're looking for.
If the uploader doesn't permit mobile viewing, then the videos can't be viewed."
"faq_activity_content6" : "If it's not working, please verify that if the screen rotation lock is off."

"faq_activity_content7" : "1) You can search for songs in the search tab
2) Tap to add to your playlist

Or

1) If you find a song you like from other playlists
2) Tap the  button to the right of the song
3) Tap "Add to another playlist" and choose the playlist to add the song to that playlist"

"faq_activity_content8" : "1) Tap the playlist you want to edit
2) Tap the button to the right of the song
3) Tap "Delete Music" to delete the song"

"faq_activity_content9" : "1) Tap in the Playlist tab
2) Enter the name of the new playlist
3) Tap "OK" to create a new playlist"

"faq_activity_content12" : "If you're using cellular networks, please switch to WIFI or move to a location with better cellular networks connection and see if it improves. If you turn off "HD Video and Audio" in More tab, it will also help!"

"faq_activity_content14" : "Free Music will not post your activity to Facebook unless you authorize it. If you login with your Facebook account and would like to automatically share your activities on Facebook, you can turn on "Post activities to Facebook" in the More tab. You can also hide your activities by turning off "Post activities to Facebook"."

"faq_activity_content15" : "If you have further questions or suggestions, please leave a message at Free Music Fan Page:https://www.facebook.com/topfreemusic or send an email to <topfreemusicteam@gmail.com>. Please also mention your device information. We will give a feedback to you as soon as possible!"

"faq_activity_content2" : "The YouTube video uploader may restrict the video by channel and by region. For example, certain videos are restricted to YouTube only or to specific regions. When this happens, you may encounter some playback issues. In that case, please try to search for other video sources."
"faq_activity_content3" : "Due to the abnormality of Facebook login system recently, the authorization page may go blank. If this happens, please restart Free Music and login again."

"faq_activity_content4" : "According to YouTube's guideline, videos must be streamed directly from YouTube, so Internet connection is required to play videos.Therefore, Free Music does NOT support downloading YouTube content for offline listening."

"faq_activity_content5" : "Please search for "keywords", then select "show all song results". You should be able to find the song you're looking for.
If the uploader doesn't permit mobile viewing, then the videos can't be viewed."
"faq_activity_content6" : "If it's not working, please verify that if the screen rotation lock is off."

"faq_activity_content7" : "1) You can search for songs in the search tab
2) Tap to add to your playlist

Or

1) If you find a song you like from other playlists
2) Tap the  button to the right of the song
3) Tap "Add to another playlist" and choose the playlist to add the song to that playlist"

"faq_activity_content8" : "1) Tap the playlist you want to edit
2) Tap the button to the right of the song
3) Tap "Delete Music" to delete the song"

"faq_activity_content9" : "1) Tap in the Playlist tab
2) Enter the name of the new playlist
3) Tap "OK" to create a new playlist"

playstore_details.title: Free Music
playstore_details.description:
Millions of Free and Trending Music
Best music & mp3 player for finding and listening trending music and music videos. With Free Music you can play music video. Play your favorite music videos right on your phone, even tablet!

Key features of Free Music:
Unlimited Free Mp3 Music 
- Search for mp3 music and music video is so easy: Look for songs from the top charts, various genres.
- Discover the latest music: Never be out of the loop
- Popular free mp3 music from Top Charts 

Feel the Power of mp3 Music
- Free streaming, mp3 music search and hits library 
- Play mp3 songs, discover music and free albums
- Watch free music video from trending artists

Take control by yourself
- Listen to artists and albums, or create your own playlist
- Easily manage your favorite music and songs
- Shuffle, Loop and Repeat mode

Easy to sync
- Support for multiple platforms: Available support on phones, tablets
- Login with you account, and immediately sync your music on other devices

More features
- Share your music, let the world know what you love to listen to
- Entirely Free Download! It will cost you nothing
- Please note that this is NOT for free music download

Free Music has more amazing features, all waiting to be discovered by you!

Any questions, please contact us via Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/topfreemusic/ or email us: topfreemusicteam@gmail.com
